    {
      "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-808f-ae2f-d03ce849ad0f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors used unsupervised and process mining approaches on the self-assessment records and found that most formative assessments were explored in preparation for the summative assessments. In general, 2 main clusters emerged and the obtained results were consistent with the self-reported strategies adopted.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-808f-ae2f-d03ce849ad0f",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
